HCPCS 

hcpcs_search(
  hcpcs    = "39503", 
  state    = "GA", 
  locality = "99",
  mac      = "10212") |> 
  remove_empty(which = c("rows", "cols")) |>
  rowwise() |>
  mutate(descriptions_clinician = map(
    descriptions_clinician, ~paste0("* ", ., collapse = "\n"))) |>
  unnest(cols = descriptions_clinician) |>
  ungroup() |> 
  display_long() |>
  gt(rowname_col = "name") |>
  northstar:::gt_style(tablign = "right", tabsize = 14)
